      • convertMultiplicityValue

        private static model.UmlMultiplicityValue convertMultiplicityValue(java.lang.String value,
                                                                   java.lang.String type)
        Converts an UmlMultiplicityValue out of a given value
        Note: If the given value is a LowerValue and is equal to the UpperValue, the value is determined by the type of the value
        Parameters:
        value - the value as a String, can be '0', '1', '*' or null
        type - the type of the value, can be 'uml:LiteralInteger' or 'uml:LiteralUnlimitedNatural'
        Returns:
        the converted UmlMultiplicityValue
